Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, you haven't been\Ntaking a bath, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised, when I moved\Nto the desk next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd take one every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor\Nin the reception office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home,\Nso make your own tea, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor? At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had a bath, either.\NHe smells almost as bad as you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...?\NUpsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is it that\NI haven't been able to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't realize that she's able to\Nmake a living at this paper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with no future,\Nthanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... My name is Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... He really is filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Doctor,\Nis this what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target of the person\Nwho's been killing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,middle-aged couples\Nthroughout Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is here in Heidelberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple is fostering a young girl,\Nand when that girl turns 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer will come to take her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does, the foster parents\Nare sure to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have no idea\Nwho that girl or her foster parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or where they live...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not delusional,\NI don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke. Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Not even the gossip rags\Nwould write up that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here\Nto get you to write it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After those twins\Nslipped out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there is at least\Na 6-month blank period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,before the brother showed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that,\Nafter leaving the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,those twins came to\NHeidelberg together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two were raised by\Nthe girl's current foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But the brother ran away from here\Nafter a short period,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving his sister behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you write a novel?\N'Course it probably won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that there is\Na missing person's report out on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And there might even be\Na newspaper article about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me check the newspapers\Nfrom nine years ago! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't allow\Nany more people to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The president has a thing against\Ncomputerization, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These are smaller versions\Nof the daily newspapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and manuscript files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are files\Nof cancelled stories and raw data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Japanese bow...?\NYou're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't have the time\Nto spend on silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave\Nwhen you're satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Every once in a while,\NI get a nut case like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please let me find something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NYou're looking well, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fainting like that...\NYou startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really didn't like\Nthe boy we hooked you up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly felt bad.\NI have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NYou don't have to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That Otto... When I talked to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that he's not\Nyour "prince on a white horse."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he didn't send you\Nany email message.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you fainted\Nbecause you saw that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I only saw him for a second,\Nso I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not it...\NI can't explain it well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't force yourself, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it felt just like\Nwhen I had that nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil"...\NIt's beginning to sound religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to a church...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems to me that\Neverything will be cleared up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if I see that person again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel that you will regain\Nthe memory you've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one means you may be\Nable to employ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you should let that\Nbe a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about your future\Nwithout stressing, is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just work up a sweat\Nplaying sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and your insecurities\Nshould disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, pull another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, were you the one\Nwho let that guy use the file room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked him\Nwhat he was doing there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said\Nyou had given him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! It's about time you... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Hey! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, isn't it?\NI always have breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go home?\NWhat about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't got one.\NMy wife left me, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife had gone back to her parents\Nwith our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about\Nbringing your wife home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who walked out!\NWhy should I go to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to regret\Nbeing so occupied with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is most important to a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wife who cannot understand that\Nis welcome to leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It was none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.\NI say that as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit saying the same thing\Nmy wife said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife was worried\Nabout your health, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sweaters used to be\Nthis tiny before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, are you really going to tell her\Nthat she's not really our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we leave it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...\NThere's no need to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy...am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the future...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gaitel may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow, your birthday, let's meet at\NHeidelberg Castle at 7:00 PM."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...at Heidelberg Castle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so busy, but here I am staring at\Na mountain of papers with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If...it's just a thought, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to go to get my wife...\NDo you think she'd come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you quit smoking, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,11 -year-old boy disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that he was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but there has been no word\Nfrom a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone named Fortner has filled out\Na missing person's report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The raw data should be\Nin here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that that killer would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,come to take his sister away\Nwhen she turned 20, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the boy in this article\Nis her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! His birth date is printed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the 20th birthday\Nof those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello, Dad? It's me.\NI just finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with a friend\Nthen I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is making preparations\Nfor a birthday party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She says she's going to meet\Na friend before coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's all grown up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe this will help me\Nto remember things...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know who I really am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you intend to do if\Nthe twin girl is at the Fortners' home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthat family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will contact the police\Nand ask for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the police will\Ndo anything just from your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late\Nafter something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen.\NIt's all in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...\NOf the four murder cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself went to\Nthe crime scene in Cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different\Nabout that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed no purpose,\Nno greed, no bitterness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like someone simply ended\Nthese people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell just by looking\Nat the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that a kid\Nwho wasn't even 20, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think a youngster could
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,kill those people\Nwithout feeling any emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't something done by a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger... What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't find the right words\Nto describe this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to describe it, it's trite,\Nbut that was the Devil's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If that killer were to appear before me,\NI would kill him without a pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street... We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NSorry to call on you so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.\NI'm Maurer of the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a newspaper reporter\Nbe wanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...I'd like to ask you\Nsome questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\N– Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regarding this missing persons report\Nthat you filed in 1936...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can forget about that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Could you please talk to us?\NDon't you have a girl living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The twin sister of\Nthe boy who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a birthday cake prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl still lives with you,\Ndoesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have raised her\Nas our true daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy had surgical scars\Non his head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl had amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner, you must contact\Nthe police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives, and your daughter's,\Nare in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She is out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going\Nto meet a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me use your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! We must\Nnotify the police first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time\Nto explain things to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the key, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll call them from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! As I said earlier,\Nhe's a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive...\NThen I'll quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow the quack's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I explain\Nthis to the police...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our daughter... Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NLet me use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line's been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Please be safe... Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past time...\NI guess that message was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to...wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to make sure\Nyou waited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to wait...\NDon't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... No, you're Nina Fortner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?\NI'm Dr. Tenma. I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. You must go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... Are you...\Nmy prince on a white horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in... Don't butt in, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I need something to tie him up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he was coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He just said\Nhe would come here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,after doing something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!\NWe've got to hurry, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...\N-Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I can't get loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! Who are you?\NAnd I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into\Nmy hospital, you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
